&lt;p&gt;As the Head of Treasury at Xendit, you will be the primary architect of our treasury engine. You will sit at the intersection of finance, product, and strategy, taking full ownership of our Treasury P&amp;amp;L and ensuring that every dollar—and every local currency—is working as profitably as possible.&lt;/p&gt;
