&lt;h3&gt;Minimum Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7-10 years of Treasury experience, with at least 3-5 years heading up Treasury in a Fintech or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience Optimizing yields on held funds (interest rate, time deposits etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience Managing FX (advising on spreads, hedging FX risk, netting strategies)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and implementing funding and liquidity strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience selecting, negotiating with and managing financial partners related to liquidity provisions (e.g., banks, debt providers)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience defining technology / tool stack for Treasury function&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and the ability to build and maintain internal and external relationships effortlessly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
