&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with stablecoins&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in managing FX risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in fast moving FinTech startup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
