&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an Internal Audit Manager to lead day-to-day audit execution in a regulated, high-volume payment business. This role sits at the core of the Internal Audit function and is responsible for converting audit plans into high-quality, actionable audit outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will manage audit engagements end-to-end, supervise audit staff, and work closely with process owners across Operations, Technology, Finance, Risk, and Compliance to assess control effectiveness and drive remediation.&lt;/p&gt;
