&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to transaction processing, system access controls, reconciliations, and operational risk is highly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional certifications (CIA, CPA, CISA) are a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
