&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy digging into processes and figuring out how things &lt;em&gt;actually&lt;/em&gt; work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can balance attention to detail with big-picture risk thinking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You communicate findings firmly but constructively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are comfortable working in fast-growing, evolving organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
